'''沃邦拦河坝'''（Barrage Vauban）是[[斯特拉斯堡|斯特拉斯堡]][[小法兰西|小法兰西]]区以西一个[[伊尔河|伊尔河]]上的一道拦河坝，兴建于1686年到1700年，设计者是法国工程师[[塞巴斯蒂安·勒普雷斯特雷·德·沃邦|塞巴斯蒂安·勒普雷斯特雷·德·沃邦]]。沃邦拦河坝高达数层，刻有雕塑，顶部有观景平台。於1971年被列為[[法国历史遗迹|法国历史遗迹]]<ref>{{Base Mérimée|PA00085039|Grande écluse de fortification dite barrage Vauban et ses abords fortifiés}}</ref><ref name=otsbv>{{cite web | url = http://www.otstrasbourg.fr/en/discover/monuments-museums-and-other-sites-to-visit/main-attractions/F223005692_the-vauban-dam-strasbourg.html | title = The Vauban Dam | publisher = Office de tourisme de Strasbourg et sa région | accessdate = 30 September 2015 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150930092443/http://www.otstrasbourg.fr/en/discover/monuments-museums-and-other-sites-to-visit/main-attractions/F223005692_the-vauban-dam-strasbourg.html | archivedate = 30 September 2015 | url-status = live}}</ref><ref name=viabv>{{cite web | url = http://www.viator.com/Strasbourg-attractions/Vauban-Dam-Barrage-Vauban/d5502-a13892 | title = Vauban Dam (Barrage Vauban) | publisher = Viator, Inc | accessdate = 30 September 2015 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150930094425/http://www.viator.com/Strasbourg-attractions/Vauban-Dam-Barrage-Vauban/d5502-a13892 | archivedate = 30 September 2015 | url-status = live}}</ref>。

